com.bluegosling.collections

Interface BiMap.BiEntry<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of keys in the map
    V - the type of values in the map
    All Superinterfaces:
    Map.Entry<K,V>
    Enclosing interface:
    BiMap<K,V>

    public static interface BiMap.BiEntry<K,V>
extends Map.Entry<K,V>
    An entry in a BiMap. Since mappings are bi-directional, this allows changing the key, which is effectively just like Map.Entry.setValue(Object) but for the other direction.
